Build script for PHP 5.2+

The goal is to create a script that will get, compile and install all dependencies of PHP 5.2+ in order they are required.

Dependencies:

sh
wget
ruby
rake


PHP dependencies for this build:

bz2
db4
curl
freetype
png
gd
gettext
imap
kerberos
ncurses
gmp
iconv
jpeg
ldap
mysql
openssl
pgsql
pspell
xmlrpc
pcre
unixODBC
xml
expat
dom
xsl
zlib
